query:
-- Buscar testes em psychometricTests que NÃO estão em testResults
SELECT 
  pt.id as psychometric_id,
  pt.testType,
  pt.employeeId,
  e.name as employeeName,
  e.employeeCode,
  pt.completedAt,
  pt.responses,
  CASE 
    WHEN tr.id IS NULL THEN 'MISSING_IN_testResults'
    ELSE 'EXISTS_IN_testResults'
  END as status
FROM psychometricTests pt
LEFT JOIN employees e ON pt.employeeId = e.id
LEFT JOIN testResults tr ON tr.employeeId = pt.employeeId AND tr.testType = pt.testType
WHERE pt.completedAt IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY pt.completedAt DESC;
